import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='ignore')
    plt.plot(data['date'], data['price'])
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Price')
    plt.title('What is the overall trend of the S&P 500 index over the given time period?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import statsmodels.api as sm
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='ignore')
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.boxplot(data['price'])
    plt.xticks([1], ['Price'])
    plt.title('What is the average daily closing price of the S&P 500 index?', wrap=True)
    median_price = data['price'].median()
    plt.axhline(y=median_price, color='r', linestyle='-', label=f'Median: {median_price:.2f}')
    plt.legend()
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
```

    plt.ylabel('Price')
    plt.title('What is the highest and lowest closing price of the S&P 500 index?')

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import statsmodels.api as sm
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import numpy as np

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='ignore')
    data = data.set_index('date')
    
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.plot(data.index, data['price'], label='Price')
    
    moving_average = data['price'].rolling(window=20).mean()
    plt.plot(data.index, moving_average, label='20-day Moving Average', linestyle='--')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax = plt.gca()
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
        plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    plt.title('What is the volatility of the S&P 500 index over the given time period?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Price')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
